Module org.opengis.geoapi
Package org.opengis.metadata.identification

Interface ServiceIdentification

All Superinterfaces:
Identification
@UML(identifier="SV_ServiceIdentification", specification=ISO_19115) public interface ServiceIdentification extends Identification
Identification of capabilities which a service provider makes available to a service user through a set of interfaces that define a behaviour - See ISO 19119 for further information.
NOTE: The prefix was MD in a previous ISO 19115 specification, but has been renamed SV in corrigendum 2006.
Since:
2.0
